<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.8">
<l>kalaivāḻ piṇaiyō ṭaṇaiyun tirunīr</l>
<l>malaivā ḻentai maruvu mūrpōl</l>
<l>ilaitāḻ teṅkiṉ mēlniṉ ṟiḷanīrk</l>
<l>kulaitāḻ kiṭaṅkiṉ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr, with ponds where hang clusters of young coconut</l>
<l>From high on coconut palms with leaves that hang [low],</l>
<l>It seems, is the city where appears our father who lives</l>
<l>In Tirunīrmalai where the stag lies with [his] mated doe.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
